sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as ODH Model Controller<br/>Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller<br/>InferenceService Reconciler
    participant IstioCP as Istio Control Plane<br/>15010/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>HTTP Scraper

    %% Flow 1: InferenceService Creation
    Note over User,IstioCP: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation (KServe Serverless with Istio)
    User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService<br/>kubectl apply -f isvc.yaml<br/>Auth: kubectl credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutating Webhook Call<br/>POST /mutate-...-inferenceservice<br/>TLS 1.2+, K8s API mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Defaulted InferenceService<br/>HTTPS Response
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validating Webhook Call<br/>POST /validate-...-inferenceservice<br/>TLS 1.2+, K8s API mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result<br/>HTTPS Response
    K8sAPI->>Controller: InferenceService Watch Event<br/>Resource Created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>IstioCP: Update Gateway Config<br/>15010/TCP gRPC<br/>mTLS Service Identity
    Controller->>IstioCP: Create VirtualService<br/>15010/TCP gRPC<br/>mTLS Service Identity
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication (mTLS)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthConfig<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodMonitor<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller-->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService Status<br/>HTTPS Response

    %% Flow 2: NIM Account Reconciliation
    Note over User,NGC: Flow 2: NIM Account Reconciliation
    User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account<br/>kubectl apply -f nim-account.yaml<br/>Auth: kubectl credentials
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validating Webhook Call<br/>POST /validate-nim-...-account<br/>TLS 1.2+, K8s API mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result<br/>HTTPS Response
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Account Watch Event<br/>Resource Created
    Controller->>NGC: Validate NGC API Key<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
    NGC-->>Controller: Validation Response<br/>HTTPS Response
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NIM ConfigMap<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServingRuntime Template<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Pull Secret<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Service Account Token
    Controller-->>K8sAPI: Update Account Status<br/>HTTPS Response

    %% Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    Note over Controller,Prometheus: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    Controller->>Controller: Expose Metrics Endpoint<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: None (TODO: secure)
    Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: None
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus Metrics<br/>HTTP Response

    %% Optional Flow: Model Registry Integration
    Note over Controller,ModelReg: Optional: Model Registry Integration
    Controller->>ModelReg: Fetch Model Metadata<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    ModelReg-->>Controller: Model Metadata<br/>JSON Response
